    {
      "instruction": "<p>Add your<strong> ground smoked paprika</strong> to a plate with a generous pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Mix everything together, then add your<strong> chicken thighs</strong> and turn them several times until they're fully coated in all the spices – this is your<strong> paprika chicken</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/Step-3-1592237822818-x200.jpg",
